{"tid":2266040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"頭套代口罩 萬聖夜逼爆 「武肺」蘭桂坊舉杯","createTime":"2020-11-01T03:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T03:29:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4b10ecbbf10f0d7d14bf4c62e289b9b4191f548b","tid":2266040,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T03:29:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201101/5RKGRLDJC5FJTCBAFF26TGZPBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201101%2F5RKGRLDJC5FJTCBAFF26TGZPBA%2F&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnhwDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=4a1154e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201101%2F5RKGRLDJC5FJTCBAFF26TGZPBA%2F&h=17d6adab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201101/5RKGRLDJC5FJTCBAFF26TGZPBA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n頭套代口罩 萬聖夜逼爆<br />\n「武肺」蘭桂坊舉杯<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎陰霾下首個萬聖節，社交距離措施亦已放寬，蘭桂坊重現久違的熱鬧，冷清了半年的酒吧坐滿暢飲的客人，可能是疫症爆發以來人數最多的一次「集會」。擠擁的遊人雖然都戴上口罩，但仍花心思裝扮成各式妖魔鬼怪，成為眾人焦點，有人更戴上武肺病毒的頭套。警員及食環署一早已預告會更嚴厲執法，前晚已有八間酒吧因違反防疫規定被檢控。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：指中聯辦宿舍個案無礙本月推措施  陳肇始拒煞停內地返港免檢疫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oEscMWdjb_mtvXD03j7NsA4nhxw=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4QAZ43PBU5E37PC7OU7C6AZ3W4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoEscMWdjb_mtvXD03j7NsA4nhxw%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4QAZ43PBU5E37PC7OU7C6AZ3W4.jpg&h=4576b313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「武肺病毒」與其他鬼怪昨晚聚集蘭桂坊舉杯暢飲。謝榮耀攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民：第時可能戴面具都唔畀<br />\n<br />\n蘭桂坊昨晚人頭湧湧，大批警員不斷在人潮中穿梭巡邏，港島總區指揮官郭柏聰亦有到場視察，警方8時實施人流管制。前來的人都表示想來感受節日氣氛，放鬆一下過去一年來沉重心情。<br />\n<br />\n打扮成西班牙電視劇《紙房子》角色的何先生表示，以往都會來蘭桂坊慶。。。。。。。。。氣氛，比想像中多人，由於已做足防疫措施，故不擔心。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：夫腦瘤命危 張竹君連月奔波威院<br />\n<br />\n「梅蘭菊竹」酒吧活動策劃總監Kenji表示，昨晚特地將酒吧佈置成具有萬聖節氣。。。。。。。。。」。他未能預計今年生意額，「但我哋都減咗價，大約100蚊一杯酒，都希望大家開心吓。」<br />\n<br />\n食環署與警方連續兩晚展開聯合行動，巡查各區酒吧，前晚巡查中共發出了54次口。。。。。。。。。。昨晚人流只及以往萬聖節的七成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/j55DA8Et9hH0qjEUKakkRwvS02c=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FTJJ5OXTOBEDLORBRGKWLESO3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fj55DA8Et9hH0qjEUKakkRwvS02c%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFTJJ5OXTOBEDLORBRGKWLESO3Q.jpg&h=8ceab746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有市民戴V煞面具，持標語聲援被扣12港青。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xWaBgNLaJtUN_IonWtL-gHKz1ag=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RTOAWHV6CBB7HDYQXJ7J75JQQA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxWaBgNLaJtUN_IonWtL-gHKz1ag%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRTOAWHV6CBB7HDYQXJ7J75JQQA.jpg&h=34e002f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■昨晚蘭桂坊的遊人絡繹不絕。"}]}